{"lemma":"خَرِيفُ","slug":"خَرِيفُ","root":"خ.ر.ف","root_slug":"خ-ر-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ر-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10402"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%81%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"autumn, fall"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"harvest"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fresh ripe dates or fruit in general"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a year, one complete agricultural cycle"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root خ ر ف (ḵ r f) meaning \"to gather produce\", \"to become ripe or attaining fullness\". Cognate with Hebrew חֹורֶף (khóref), Sabaean and Qatabanian Old South Arabian 𐩭𐩧𐩰 (ḫrf), Mehri ḫarf, Shehri ḫorf, Soqotri ḥorf, Harsusi ḫōref, Ge'ez ኀሪፍ (ḫärif)."},"ipa":["/xa.riːf/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10402","headword_ar":"خَرِيفٌ","root":"xrf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"Fresh ripe dates, (K, TA,) or fruits [in general], (S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gathered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plucked;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxoruwfN","text_ar":"مَخْرُوفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA. See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxorafN","text_ar":"مَخْرَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence. [And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurofapN","text_ar":"خُرْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b2-  And hence, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fresh"},{"kind":"text","text":"milk; milk"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recently drawn from the udder."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Hr, TA.) ―         -b3-  Palm-trees ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naxolN","text_ar":"نَخْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whereof the quantity of the fruit that is upon them is computed by conjecture."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraAy^ifu","text_ar":"خَرَايِفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xariyfapN","text_ar":"خَرِيفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b4-  [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"autumn;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of the divisions of the year,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh,) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"division"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consisting of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three months between the end of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qayoZ","text_ar":"قَيْظ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"summer"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the beginning of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$itaA='","text_ar":"شِتَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"winter"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Lth, K, *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which the fruits are gathered."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, S, Mgh, Msb, K.) ―         -b5-  And hence, (Mgh, TA,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A year:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, K, TA:) so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano SaAma yawomFA fiY sabiyli A@ll~`hi baAEadahu A@ll~`hu mina","text_ar":"مَنْ صَامَ يَوْمًا فِى سَبِيلِ ا@للّٰهِ بَاعَدَهُ ا@للّٰهُ مِنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAri A^arobaEiyna xariyfFA A^awo saboEiyna","text_ar":"النَّارِ اَرْبَعِينَ خَرِيفًا اَوْ سَبْعِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whoso fasteth a day in the way of God, God will remove him from the fire"},{"kind":"text","text":"of Hell]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the distance of a journey of forty years, or seventy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh: and similar exs. are given in the TA, from three trads.: see also an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a","text_ar":"اـِنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b6-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rain of the season so called:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK,) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first of the rain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the beginning of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$itaA='","text_ar":"شِتَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"winter"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (JK, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which comes at the time of the cutting off of the fruit of the palmtrees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"then follows the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wasomiY~","text_ar":"وَسْمِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", at the coming in of the winter; then, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabiyE","text_ar":"رَبِيع"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sayof","text_ar":"صَيْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and then, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamiym","text_ar":"حَمِيم"},{"kind":"text","text":": so says As: El-Ghanawee says that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xryf","text_ar":"خريف"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"auroral"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rising of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~iEoraY","text_ar":"الشِّعْرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sirius,"},{"kind":"text","text":"which commenced, in central Arabia, about the epoch of the Flight, on"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the 13th of July, O. S.,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"auroral"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"setting of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEaroquwataAni","text_ar":"العَرْقُوَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfarogaAni","text_ar":"الفَرْغَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the 26th and 27th of the Mansions of the Moon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"commencing, in the same region and period, on"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the 8th and 21st of Sept., O. S.,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and continuing thirteen days]: El-Ghowr and Rekeeyeh [? (imperfectly written)] and El- Hijáz are all rained upon by the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xryf","text_ar":"خريف"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but Nejd is not: AZ says, the first rain is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wasomiY~","text_ar":"وَسْمِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the follows the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$atawiY~","text_ar":"شَتَوِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafay^iY~","text_ar":"دَفَيِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sayof","text_ar":"صَيْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamiym","text_ar":"حَمِيم"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xariyf","text_ar":"خَرِيف"},{"kind":"text","text":": and therefore the year is made to consist of six seasons: accord. to AHn, [who seems in this matter to differ from most others,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxryf","text_ar":"الخريف"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not originally the name of the division of the year; but the name of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the rain of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qayoZ","text_ar":"قَيْظ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"summer"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and then the season was named thereby. (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawo'N","text_ar":"نَوْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b7-  [Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage of the season so called,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the rain so called;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabiyEN","text_ar":"رَبِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the “ herbage of the season, or of the rain, so called. ” So in the phrase used by Khálid Ibn-Jebeleh (in explaining the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaruwf","text_ar":"خَرُوف"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA","text_ar":"مَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raEaY Alxariyfa","text_ar":"رَعَى الخَرِيفَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such as pastures upon the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xryf","text_ar":"خريف"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b8-  Also, accord. to AA, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A rivulet, streamlet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small channel for irrigation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","Mgh","Msb","JK"]}]}}